    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >对抗炫目多彩的外星浪潮</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在宇宙探索途中，你将遭遇各类外星物种。熟练掌握移动、射击与技能操作，应对一轮比一轮更强的敌人进攻。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/e5b39bc7ee7489b6356d9a80c3b37002.poster.avif?t=1770571008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/e5b39bc7ee7489b6356d9a80c3b37002.webm?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/e5b39bc7ee7489b6356d9a80c3b37002.mp4?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 探索宇宙深处 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局游戏都呈现出一个充满新奇与发现的宇宙。在外星人进攻的间隙，从附近星球采集资源，为下一场战斗做好准备。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/ad0c1e7585f9e53c64a474abfb1af5ae.poster.avif?t=1770571008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/ad0c1e7585f9e53c64a474abfb1af5ae.webm?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/ad0c1e7585f9e53c64a474abfb1af5ae.mp4?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 打造制胜之道 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的飞船，并策略性地搭配神器、天赋和物品。游戏拥有无数构筑组合，让你自由定义玩法风格，确保每次游玩都独一无二、乐趣十足。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/94fde4f5fb53927596e1c946a83e151e.poster.avif?t=1770571008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/94fde4f5fb53927596e1c946a83e151e.webm?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/94fde4f5fb53927596e1c946a83e151e.mp4?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/94c4b3e21e6e7d595e3a0e38e5b62010.poster.avif?t=1770571008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/94c4b3e21e6e7d595e3a0e38e5b62010.webm?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/94c4b3e21e6e7d595e3a0e38e5b62010.mp4?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/11bf0d780ebd4195df74cfe8f3850003.poster.avif?t=1770571008\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/11bf0d780ebd4195df74cfe8f3850003.webm?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352670/extras/11bf0d780ebd4195df74cfe8f3850003.mp4?t=1770571008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色 </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>无限重玩性</strong>: 动态生成的宇宙，包含无数星球、恒星、黑洞、外星生命与神秘奇观，打破传统静态或重复性地图的局限。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富构筑系统</strong>: 通过天赋、物品、神器等获得数百种能力，自由组合，彻底改变战斗方式与游戏策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>策略性玩法:</strong> 在每轮外星人进攻之间，采集资源、探索宇宙，为下一步行动做好计划。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>快速游戏节奏:</strong> 支持短时间游玩，可随时中断并继续当前进度，灵活应对生活节奏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>更多精彩内容: 任务、可解锁内容与诸多惊喜，等你发掘。</strong> </p></li></ul>",
